{"title_page": "Foc (Barcelona Metro)", "text_new": "{{Infobox station\n| name            = Foc\n| type            = [[Barcelona Metro]] [[rapid transit]] station\n| style           = \n| image           = foc andana.png\n| image_caption   = Upper platform of the station\n| address         = Passeig de la Zona Franca with Carrer del Foc, [[Barcelona]]\n| country         = \n| coordinates     = {{coord|41|21|22|N|2|08|30|E|region:ES-CT_type:landmark_source:kolossus-nlwiki|display=inline,title}}\n| line            = \n| other           = \n| structure       = Underground\n| platform        = \n| depth           = \n| levels          = \n| tracks          = \n| parking         = \n| bicycle         = \n| baggage_check   = \n| opened          = 8 September 2018\n| closed          = \n| rebuilt         = \n| electrified     = \n| ADA             = \n| code            = \n| owned           = [[Transports Metropolitans de Barcelona]]\n| zone            = 1 ([[Autoritat del Transport Metropolit\u00e0|ATM]])\n| smartcardname   = \n| smartcardstatus = \n| former          = \n| passengers      = \n| pass_year       = \n| pass_percent    = \n| pass_system     = \n| mpassengers     = \n| services        = {{S-rail|title=Barcelona Metro}}\n{{S-line|system=Barcelona Metro|line=L10S|previous=Zona Franca|next=Foneria}}\n| map_type        = Spain Barcelona#Spain\n| map_caption     = Location in Barcelona##Location in Spain\n}}\n\n'''Foc''' is a [[Barcelona Metro]] station located in the [[Zona Franca]] neighborhood of the [[Barcelona]] municipality, served by [[Barcelona Metro line 10|line L10]].<ref name=planbcn>{{cite web | url = http://w20.bcn.cat/GuiaMap//default.aspx#x=26371&y=80231&z=5&c=K001&w=1380&h=830&base=GuiaMartorell | title = Pl\u00e0nolbcn | publisher = Ajuntament de Barcelona | language = Catalan | accessdate = 2015-02-03}}</ref><ref name=tmap>{{cite web | url = http://cartometro.com/cartes/metro-tram-barcelona/ | title = Track map of the Barcelona Metro | publisher = cartometro.com | accessdate = 2015-02-03}}</ref>\n\nThe station is located underneath the ''Passeig de la Zona Franca''.\n\nThe station opened on 8 September 2018,<ref name=LaVanguardia>{{cite web | url = http://www.lavanguardia.com/local/barcelona/20180612/4553358329/estaciones-linea-10-sud-metro-foc-foneria-inauguracion.html | title = Las obras del metro a la Zona Franca encaran la recta final | publisher = La Vanguardia | language = Spanish | accessdate = 2018-06-15}}</ref> when line L10 opened from [[Collblanc (Barcelona Metro)|Collblanc station]] to this station, as a terminal. Eventually trains will run through this station in service as the rest of L10 is brought into service.\n\n[[File:foc exposicio.png|thumb|centre|Exhibition room located between lobby and platforms]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{commonscat-inline|Foc metrostation}}\n\n{{Barcelona Metro line 10}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Foc Cisell (Barcelona Metro)}}\n[[Category:Barcelona Metro line 10 stations]]\n[[Category:Transport in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 2018]]\n\n\n{{Spain-railstation-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox station\n| name            = Foc\n| type            = [[Barcelona Metro]] [[rapid transit]] station\n| style           = \n| image           = foc andana.png\n| image_caption   = Upper platform of the station\n| address         = Passeig de la Zona Franca with Carrer del Foc, [[Barcelona]]\n| country         = \n| coordinates     = {{coord|41|21|22|N|2|08|30|E|region:ES-CT_type:landmark_source:kolossus-nlwiki|display=inline,title}}\n| line            = \n| other           = \n| structure       = Underground\n| platform        = \n| depth           = \n| levels          = \n| tracks          = \n| parking         = \n| bicycle         = \n| baggage_check   = \n| opened          = 8 September 2018\n| closed          = \n| rebuilt         = \n| electrified     = \n| ADA             = \n| code            = \n| owned           = [[Transports 