o line 10}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Foc Cisell (Barcelona Metro)}}\n[[Category:Barcelona Metro line 10 stations]]\n[[Category:Transport in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 2018]]\n\n\n{{Spain-railstation-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Carto.metro", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:Update link to cartometro.com (301:permanent move)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foc_(Barcelona_Metro)"}
