b-head-scarf-protest-tehran/29013882.html |archive-date=2 February 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"theguardian.com_2\">{{cite web|author=[[Saeed Kamali Dehghan|Dehghan, Saeed Kamali]]|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/feb/02/tehran-hijab-protest-iranian-police-arrest-29-women|title=Tehran hijab protest: Iranian police arrest 29 women|work=The Guardian|date=2 February 2018|accessdate=2 February 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202070248/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/feb/02/tehran-hijab-protest-iranian-police-arrest-29-women|archive-date=2 February 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"aljazeera.com_1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/02/iran-arrests-29-women-wearing-hijab-protests-180202084416823.html|title=Iran arrests 29 women for not wearing hijab in protests|publisher=[[Aljazeera.com]]|date=2 February 2018|accessdate=4 February 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203215435/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/02/iran-arrests-29-women-wearing-hijab-protests-180202084416823.html|archive-date=3 February 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"amnesty.org_1\">{{cite web |url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2018/02/iran-at-least-six-young-human-rights-defenders-arrested-in-coordinated-raids-at-risk-of-torture/ |title=Iran: At least six young human rights defenders arrested in coordinated raids at risk of torture |publisher=Amnesty International |date=2 February 2018 |accessdate=16 February 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216205323/https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2018/02/iran-at-least-six-young-human-rights-defenders-arrested-in-coordinated-raids-at-risk-of-torture/ |archive-date=16 February 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"thenational.ae_1\">{{cite web|url=https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/iran-cracks-down-on-women-protesting-against-headscarves-1.701223|title=Iran cracks down on women protesting against headscarves|publisher=[[The Nation